{"TopicId":223034,"ForumId":130,"TopicTitle":"HideVAB (0.2.0)","CreatedByName":"JakeInABoat","CreatedById":232238,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-16T01:58:12Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"JakeInABoat","CreatedById":232238,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-16T01:58:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHideVAB allows you to show / hide the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E while constructing your craft. This allows for much greater freedom of movement and easier construction of large craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/JakeInABoat/HideVAB\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/JakeInABoat/HideVAB\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLicense:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.en.html\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EGPLv3\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDownload via \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Comprehensive Kerbal Archive Network (a KSP mod manager)\u0022\u003ECKAN\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E,\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3547/HideVAB\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Espacedock\u003C/a\u003E, or\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/JakeInABoat/HideVAB\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Egithub\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-01-20T01:59:35Z\u0022 title=\u002201/20/2024 01:59  AM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jan 20\u0022\u003EJanuary 20\u003C/time\u003E by JakeInABoat\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alewx","CreatedById":102791,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-18T10:33:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes this also avoid the size limits of the crafts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JakeInABoat","CreatedById":232238,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-18T14:36:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224360109\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221705574015\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022102791\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alewx\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, Alewx said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDoes this also avoid the size limits of the crafts?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are no limits in KSP2 currently.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCurrently this mod simply hides the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E geometry and extends the cameras bounds making it a bit easier to\u00A0 move around and work on large craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alewx","CreatedById":102791,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-19T16:30:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224360133\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221705588598\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022232238\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JakeInABoat\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/18/2024 at 3:36 PM, JakeInABoat said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are no limits in KSP2 currently.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCurrently this mod simply hides the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E geometry and extends the cameras bounds making it a bit easier to\u00A0 move around and work on large craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh nice ok, I was thinking that it was mentioned that you can build bigger crafts in ksp2 but they would still be limited to the size of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JakeInABoat","CreatedById":232238,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-20T01:47:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHideVAB 0.2.0 now available.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\u0022background-color:#22272e;color:#adbac7;font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nAdded a background / backdrop when the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E is hidden for a consistent (and hopefully more pleasant) visual experience (WIP).\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLeave the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E floor un-hidden to give a reference point and for visual purposes.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nMuch code cleanup and refactoring should be more robust against changing scenes / toggling blueprint mode.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xav","CreatedById":232341,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-22T04:56:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224360133\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221705588598\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022232238\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JakeInABoat\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/19/2024 at 1:36 AM, JakeInABoat said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are no limits in KSP2 currently.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCurrently this mod simply hides the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E geometry and extends the cameras bounds making it a bit easier to\u00A0 move around and work on large craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthere is a limit, if it goes outside the bounds of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E, you cant launch it.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://pasteboard.co/EqdGRfmSunxF.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://pasteboard.co/EqdGRfmSunxF.png\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://pasteboard.co/5GV8SoDwMuFd.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://pasteboard.co/5GV8SoDwMuFd.png\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JakeInABoat","CreatedById":232238,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-23T16:03:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224361033\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221705899405\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022232341\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xav\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/21/2024 at 11:56 PM, Xav said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthere is a limit, if it goes outside the bounds of the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E, you cant launch it.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://pasteboard.co/EqdGRfmSunxF.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://pasteboard.co/EqdGRfmSunxF.png\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://pasteboard.co/5GV8SoDwMuFd.png\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://pasteboard.co/5GV8SoDwMuFd.png\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAha, ok I see. Yes, currently HideVAB does not do anything about that. I may look into it though, so far has not been a limitation for me though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}